{"tid":1471241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非係時候諗諗計 提下你身邊善忘嘅香港人","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T09:02:57.000Z","uid":205105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"63d04a0b1fa6b992998b4b495a7bee139f4d69f2","tid":1471241,"uid":205105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"代個friend出post，集思廣益<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有個小提議, 唔知work唔work, 大家入嚟研究下&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n1) 諗下係主要受影響地區做街站可唔可行<br />\n搵啲人喺元朗嗰度做直播街訪, 走去問啲市民對地區嘅第一身感受, 講下對政府同警方信心問題<br />\n&ldquo;而家如果元朗黑社會打嚟你夠唔夠膽報警&rdquo;<br />\n如果可以, 區區做都得<br />\n<br />\n2) 眾籌元朗站地鐵廣告<br />\n目的係激起市民大眾思考<br />\n&ldquo;如果而家元朗白衫黑社會逼你俾錢, 你夠唔夠膽唔俾呀？你夠唔夠膽報警？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;如果元朗白衫黑社會撩你老婆、你可以點做？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;如果元朗白衫軍打你？、你可以點做？報警？&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;你唔係住北角, 唔係住荃灣, 唔係住元朗. 但你真係覺得可以唔關自己事？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n希望啲人明白到, 再唔反抗, 問題會變成恆常<br />\n已經再唔係學生要去爭取啲乜嘢. 而係警黑合作, 政府唔干預, 今日可以無厘頭打得你,聽日可以搵黑社會收你間屋, 同時你同邊個講<br />\n<br />\n喺太古葵芳, 放完催淚彈, 隨意攻擊市民,冇責任,冇底線<br />\n好多你以為唔會發生, 去到今日已經出現<br />\n無論你幾有錢, 乜嘢社會地位, 攬住層樓以為與世無爭, 平安開開心心食飯, 唔想參與唔想知道<br />\n, 拆遷戶、趕絕低端人口、新疆教育營都可以發生喺你身上<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"eb60b20069fff7cbd129801c02aa22cce46fa5d0","tid":1471241,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2007256be91b16f350dd91fee61f4e465530232","tid":1471241,"uid":205105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:28:19.000Z","msg":"我自己咁睇<br />\n將近月發生嘅事不斷喺社區討論，迫唔睇新聞嘅人都要吸收資訊，要呢d 事𣎴斷發酵，拖到9月開學拖到區選<br />\n當大家都知發生緊咩事，明白前文後理嘅市民多左，幫口嘅街坊都會更多（雖然而家已經有好多區覺醒左，黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />將軍澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美孚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n但仲有好多地方街坊需要扶一把<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158f7425cbbfeaf91d2c99bcf462edee99fbe60e","tid":1471241,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:30:52.000Z","msg":"818<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人</span>大遊行<br />\n和理非勇武缺一不可<br />\nUnited we stand, d